Text: Speaking at Rice Econ class Cc I have spoken with the instructor of my Economics of Energy class here at Rice and passed on your contact information to him He is interested in having you speak before our class and will I believe be in contact with you soon I am enclosing in this email the contact information for him Thank you again for the use of your valuable time both during the interview process of which I am very eagerly awaiting the results and now I am extremely excited about the prospect of working at Enron during the coming summer INSTRUCTOR INFO Ken Medlock Sincerely Phil Mayor
